</li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>setUTCFullYear()</code></strong> 方法根据世界标准时间为一个具体日期设置年份。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/date-setutcfullyear.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>dateObj</var>.setUTCFullYear(<var>yearValue</var>[, <var>monthValue</var>[, <var>dayValue</var>]])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"yearvalue\"><code>yearValue</code></dt>\n <dd>指定年份整数值，例如，1995</dd>\n <dt id=\"monthvalue\"><code>monthValue</code></dt>\n <dd>可选。指定一个 0-11 之间的整数值，代表从一月到十二月。</dd>\n <dt id=\"dayvalue\"><code>dayValue</code></dt>\n <dd>可选。指定一个 1-31 之间的整数值，代表月份中的第几天。如果你指定了 dayValue 参数，那么你必须指定 monthValue 参数。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"描述","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如果你没有指定具体的 <code>monthValue</code> 和 <code>dayValue</code>，将会使用&nbsp;<code>getUTCMonth</code>&nbsp;和 <code>getUTCDate</code>&nbsp;方法的返回值。</p>\n\n<p>如果你指定的参数超出了期待范围，<code>setUTCFullYear() 方法将会根据 Date 对象，更新其他参数和日期信息。例如，如果你将 monthValue 设定为 15，年份会增加 1，月份值则为为 3。</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用_setutcfullyear()","title":"使用 <code>setUTCFullYear()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> theBigDay <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setUTCFullYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1997</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"使用 setUTCFullYear()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范版本</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注解</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%201st%20edition,%20June%201997.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>初始定义。 在 JavaScript 1.3 实施。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.9.5.41\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-date.prototype.setutcfullyear\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-date.prototype.setutcfullyear\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Date.setUTCFullYear","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCFullYear/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>相关连接</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCFullYear()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setFullYear()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"描述","id":"描述"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"setUTCFullYear() 方法根据世界标准时间为一个具体日期设置年份。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/date/setutcfullyear","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/